People love to ask me why I became a dietitian. I weren’t always sure why&hellip;
I am not even always sure that I chose it as much as it chose me&hellip;
When I look back it is as if life was always busy preparing me for that day&hellip; I grew up on a farm in the northern regions of South Africa. As a child I had the opportunity to regularly eat fresh home grown food.
